description:
The API Development Toolkit for Enterprises.

Develop and test APIs with a wide range of features, Postman compatibility; available as a Cloud or Offline solution. What more could you ask for?
We have released Testfully Desktop 1.186.0 with several new features, improvements, and bug fixes. This release includes a new tab experience, ability to zoom in and out of the app using shortcut keys, new in-app notification system, and more. For a full list of changes, please see the changelog at https://testfully.io/changelog
